The best western has a seasonal outdoor pool only, which is no good in December.	The pool was closed as it is outdoor and opens in the spring.	Also to our delight there was a fitness centre, swimming pool and a sauna.	There is also an outdoor pool on the 3rd floor.	Swimming pool only open when lifeguard is there from 10a to 9p.	The only thing I did not like about this property is the lack of a indoor swimming pool or even a hot tub.	Also disappointed that pool was only outdoor/seasonal.	The kids had a blast in the pool and the lifeguard there was amazing.